ine McGraw Voices Key Character In Disney/Pixar Sequel|first=N'Duke|last=Amanda|date=March 22, 2019|accessdate=March 22, 2019|work=[[Deadline Hollywood|Deadline]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190323000135/https://deadline.com/2019/03/toy-story-4-madeleine-mcgraw-disney-pixar-movie-1202581180/|archive-date=March 23, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n* [[Christina Hendricks]] as [[List of Toy Story characters#Gabby Gabby|Gabby Gabby]]<ref name=\"auto1\">{{cite web|url=https://www.slashfilm.com/new-toy-story-4-cast-members-and-characters/|title=Meet the New 'Toy Story 4' Characters Voiced by Keanu Reeves, Christina Hendricks & Ally Maki|date=March 19, 2019|website=/Film|access-date=March 19, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190328165249/https://www.slashfilm.com/new-toy-story-4-cast-members-and-characters/|archive-date=March 28, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n* [[Keanu Reeves]] as [[List of Toy Story characters#Duke Caboom|Duke Caboom]]<ref name=\"TS4Keanu\">{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2018/11/tim-allen-toy-story-4-cast-includes-keanu-reeves-1202508084/|title=Tim Allen: 'Toy Story 4' Cast Includes Keanu Reeves|first=Geoff|last=Boucher|date=November 22, 2018|accessdate=November 22, 2018|work=[[Deadline Hollywood|Deadline]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181123005841/https://deadline.com/2018/11/tim-allen-toy-story-4-cast-includes-keanu-reeves-1202508084/|archive-date=November 23, 2018|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name=\"trailer pr\">{{cite web | url = https://comicbook.com/movies/2019/03/19/toy-story-4-keanu-reeves-duke-caboom-confirmed-disney-pixar/ | title = 'Toy Story 4': Disney Confirms Keanu Reeves' Role | first = Charlie | last = Ridgley | date = March 19, 2019 | accessdate = March 19, 2019 | work = Comicbook.com | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190320153044/https://comicbook.com/movies/2019/03/19/toy-story-4-keanu-reeves-duke-caboom-confirmed-disney-pixar/ | archive-date = March 20, 2019 | url-status = live }}<