-golden-globes-nominations-full-list-1259626 |title=Golden Globes: Full List of Nominations |website=[[The Hollywood Reporter]] |access-date=December 9, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191210132833/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/2020-golden-globes-nominations-full-list-1259626 |archive-date=December 10, 2019 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[Hollywood Critics Association]]\n| rowspan=\"2\"|  January 9, 2020\n| Best Animated Film\n| ''Toy Story 4''\n| {{won}}\n|  rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\" |<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.nextbestpicture.com/latest/the-2019-hollywood-critics-association-hca-nominations |title=The 2019 Hollywood Critics Association (HCA) Nominations |last=Boucher |first=Geoff |publisher=Next Best Picture |date=November 26, 2019 |accessdate=November 25, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200102170350/https://www.nextbestpicture.com/latest/the-2019-hollywood-critics-association-hca-nominations |archive-date=January 2, 2020 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|-\n| Best Animated or VFX Performance\n| [[Tom Hanks]]\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Critics' Choice Movie Award]]s\n| [[25th Critics' Choice Awards|January 12, 2020]]\n| [[Critics' Choice Movie Award for Best Animated Feature|Best Animated Feature]]\n| ''Toy Story 4''\n| {{won}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.criticschoice.com/critics-choice-awards/|title=25th Critics' Choice Awards|accessdate=December 8, 2019|date=December 8, 2019|publisher=[[Critics' Choice Awards]]|type=Press release|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161224125043/http://www.criticschoice.com/critics-choice-awards/|archive-date=December 24, 2016|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[American Cinema Editors]]\n| January 17, 2020\n| [[American Cinema Editors Award for Best Edited Animated Feature Film]]\n| Axel Geddes\n| {{Won}}\n| align=center| <ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.thewrap.com/american-cinema-editors-nominate-parasite-jojo-rabbit-