n' as top films in 2019|date=2019-12-09|website=mlive|language=en|access-date=2019-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191211101151/https://www.mlive.com/michigansbest/2019/12/detroit-film-critics-society-names-parasite-marriage-story-the-irishman-as-top-films-in-2019.html|archive-date=December 11, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[San Diego Film Critics Society Awards]]\n| December 9, 2019\n| [[San Diego Film Critics Society Award for Best Animated Film|Best Animated Film]]\n| Josh Cooley\n| {{draw|Runner-up}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.awardscircuit.com/2019/12/09/san-diego-film-critics-society-winners-the-irishman-wins-picture-safdie-brothers-take-director/|title=23rd San Diego Film Critics Society Awards|accessdate=10 December 2019|date=9 December 2019|publisher=[[San Diego Film Critics Society]]|type=Press release|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191210140028/https://www.awardscircuit.com/2019/12/09/san-diego-film-critics-society-winners-the-irishman-wins-picture-safdie-brothers-take-director/|archive-date=December 10, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Chicago Film Critics Association]]\n| December 14, 2019\n| [[Chicago Film Critics Association Award for Best Animated Film|Best Animated Film]]\n| ''Toy Story 4''\n| {{Won}}\n|\n|-\n| [[St. Louis Film Critics Association Awards]]\n| December 15, 2019\n| [[St. Louis Gateway Film Critics Association Award for Best Animated Film|Best Animated Feature]]\n| ''Toy Story 4''\n| {{Won}}\n|\n|-\n| [[Dallas\u2013Fort Worth Film Critics Association]]\n| December 16, 2019\n| [[Dallas\u2013Fort Worth Film Critics Association Award for Best Animated Film|Best Animated Film]]\n| ''Toy Story 4''\n| {{Won}}\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[Satellite Award]]s\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[24th Satellite Awards|December 19, 2019]]\n| [[Satellite Award for Best Animated or Mixed Media Feature|Best Animated or Mixed Media Feature]]\n| Josh Cooley\n| {{nom}}\n| rowspan=\"2\" style=\"te