el Geddes\n| {{Won}}\n| align=center| <ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.thewrap.com/american-cinema-editors-nominate-parasite-jojo-rabbit-knives-out-for-top-awards/|title=70th ACE Eddie Awards|accessdate=11 December 2019|date=11 December 2019|publisher=thewrap|type=Press release|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191211153450/http://www.thewrap.com/american-cinema-editors-nominate-parasite-jojo-rabbit-knives-out-for-top-awards/|archive-date=December 11, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Producers Guild of America Award]]s\n| [[Producers Guild of America Awards 2019|January 18, 2020]]\n| [[Producers Guild of America Award for Best Animated Motion Picture|Outstanding Producer of Animated Theatrical Motion Pictures]]\n| Mark Nielsen and [[Jonas Rivera]]\n| {{Won}}\n| align=center| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2020/film/news/pga-awards-winners-2020-1203471639/|title=PGA Awards Winners: Complete List|website=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|first=Adam|last=B. Vary|date=January 18, 2020|accessdate=January 19, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Motion Picture Sound Editors|Golden Reel Awards]]\n| January 19, 2020\n| Outstanding Achievement in Sound Editing \u2013 Feature Animation\n| Leff Lefferts, Jeremy Bowker, [[Randy Thom]], Bjorn Ole Schroeder, Samson Neslund, David Farmer, [[Michael Silvers]], Larry Oatfield, Chris Manning, Shelley Roden, John Roesch\n| {{Won}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite news|url=https://deadline.com/2019/12/motion-pictures-sound-editors-67th-annual-golden-reel-nominations-1202809902/|title=Motion Picture Sound Editors Unveil 67th Annual Golden Reel Nominations|work=Deadline Hollywood|accessdate=December 27, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Humanitas Prize]]\n| January 24, 2020\n| Feature Film, Family\n| [[John Lasseter]] (Story), [[Andrew Stanton]] (Story and Screenplay), Josh Cooley (Story), Valerie LaPointe (Story), [[Rashida Jones]] (Story), [[Will McCormack]] (Story), [[Martin Hynes]] (Story) and Stephany Folsom (Story and Screenpla