er 2011, during the tournament, it was decided that if two teams from the same country make the semi-finals they would be paired in the semi-final so there would be no national final.<ref>{{cite web|title=Who meet who in the semis.|url=http://www.conmebol.com/libertadoresfemenina/Copa-Libertadores-Femenina-resultados-y-cuadro-del-torneo-20111121-0007.html|publisher=CONMEBOL|accessdate=22 November 2011|language=Spanish|date=21 November 2011}}</ref>\n\n{{Round4-with third\n<!--Date-Place|Team 1|Score 1|Team 2|Score 2 -->\n<!--semi-finals -->\n|24 November 2011|'''{{flagicon|CHI}} [[Colo-Colo (women)|Colo Colo]]'''| '''4''' |{{flagicon|VEN|football}} [[Caracas FC|Caracas]] | 1\n|24 November 2011|{{flagicon|BRA}} [[Santos FC (ladies)|Santos]]|1|'''{{flagicon|BRA}} [[S\u00e3o Jos\u00e9 Esporte Clube (women)|S\u00e3o Jos\u00e9]]'''|'''2'''\n<!--final -->\n|27 November 2011|{{flagicon|CHI}} [[Colo-Colo (women)|Colo Colo]]| 0 |'''{{flagicon|BRA}} [[S\u00e3o Jos\u00e9 Esporte Clube (women)|S\u00e3o Jos\u00e9]]'''| '''1'''\n<!--third place -->\n|27 November 2011|{{flagicon|VEN}} [[Caracas FC|Caracas]]| 0 |'''{{flagicon|BRA}} [[Santos FC (ladies)|Santos]]'''| '''6'''\n}}\n\n===Semifinals===\n{{footballbox\n|date = 24 November 2011\n|time = 16:00 [[UTC\u221202:00]]\n|team1 = [[Colo-Colo (women)|Colo Colo]] {{flagicon|CHI}}\n|score = 4\u20131\n|report = [http://mundodelfutbolfemenino.blogspot.com/2011/11/sao-jose-vencio-santos-y-jugara-final.html Report]\n|team2 = {{flagicon|VEN|football}} [[Caracas FC|Caracas]]\n|goals1 = [[B\u00e1rbara Santib\u00e1\u00f1ez|Santib\u00e1\u00f1ez]] {{goal|29||32}}<br> [[Yanara Aedo|Aedo]] {{goal|46}}<br> [[Soleidys Rengel|Rengel]] {{goal|71|o.g.}}\n|goals2 = [[Ysaura Viso|Viso]] {{goal|16}}\n|stadium = [[Est\u00e1dio Martins Pereira]], [[S\u00e3o Jos\u00e9 dos Campos]]\n|attendance = \n|referee = \n}}\n{{footballbox\n|date = 24 November 2011\n|time = 18:30 [[UTC\u221202:00]]\n|team1 = [[Santos FC (ladies)|Santos]] {{flagicon|BRA}}\n|score = 1\u20